name: Dominate the game
description:
"Domine le jeu" ~Dominate the game is a digital collage (1080x1350 pixels in jpg) created in december 2018 from digital artist and graphic designer Neojvngle.
First release on Instagram and then archived. It was lastly shown on an exhibition in September 2020 [ https://fb.me/e/dhR63PxGp ].

Bringing it back to you on very limited edition, this is also my first NFT. This poster is still one of my favorite 3 years later... However, I still have a lot of amazing work to share.
